          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Greater Leadership Overseas for the Benefit of Equality Act of 2018 or the GLOBE Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of State to include information about the treatment of lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender, and intersex (LGBTI) individuals in its annual report on human rights in foreign countries. The bill also contains other provisions to protect LGBTI rights, including provisions barring foreign individuals who commit serious human rights violations against LGBTI individuals from entering the United States. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-12-13T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
